Phase 4: embeddings provider, related knowledge, Daily Brief

- src/lib/embeddings: pluggable provider (OpenAI default, Voyage AI fallback)
  honoring EMBEDDINGS_PROVIDER + EMBEDDINGS_MODEL env vars
- backfill.ts: embeds existing articles and document_chunks in batches, idempotent
- Auto-embed in syncFeed: new articles get embedded inline; failures are quiet
  so missing API keys never break ingestion
- POST /api/embeddings/backfill: trigger backfill on demand (limit query param)
- GET /api/related?articleId=: cosine-similarity search over article + chunk
  embeddings, excludes the source article, threshold 0.35
- RelatedPanel mounted at the bottom of the article reader; hides itself if
  the API key isn't configured or nothing is similar enough
- GET /api/brief: Anthropic streaming endpoint with prompt caching on the
  article block; Sonnet 4.6, temperature 0.4
- /today page: streams the brief, has a Regenerate button

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 <noreply@anthropic.com>
